pendence of\nconcentrations and subhalo annihilation, which would erroneously lead to very\nlarge boost factors (a few hundred for galaxy halos and over 1000 for\nclusters).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Jan 2013 21:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 Apr 2013 13:38:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
