etic simulations, the results show that our proposed protocol\nsignificantly outperforms D3 and MPTCP in terms of the precision at K and the\nsum of application-level importance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Feb 2013 15:44:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-02-04"}
